description:
Photography and post-processing using onOne's Perfect Photo Suite 8

This course features start-to-finish examples on photographing and post-processing photographs using onOne Software's Perfect Photo Suite 8. Nicole shares everything, including behind-the-scenes photos, her thought-process, and even some of the "outtake" images, as she works her way through ten images.

At the end of this course, you will be able to:

  • Replace a boring sky
  • Add texture to an image
  • Mask two images together
  • Create and save your own presets
  • ... and more!
title: Light & Process: onOne Software
